Package io.github.jidcoo.opto.lcdb.enhancer.core.proxy

Class DebugEnhancerProxy

java.lang.Object
io.github.jidcoo.opto.lcdb.enhancer.LeetcodeJavaDebugEnhancer
io.github.jidcoo.opto.lcdb.enhancer.core.proxy.DebugEnhancerProxy
public final class DebugEnhancerProxy extends LeetcodeJavaDebugEnhancer

DebugEnhancerProxy is a static proxy class used to enhance and intercept the functionality of LeetcodeJavaDebugEnhancer.

In versions 1.0.2 and later, all new feature implementations will be based on it. DebugEnhancerProxy intercepts and processes methods with DebugEnhancerProxy.ProxyPoint as an enhanced granularity.

Since:
1.0.2
Author:
Jidcoo
